{
  "stem": "11964.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was one occurrence that I would like to mention that happened there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I told you that I had a makeshift, clandestine school in Radomsko in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were many girls there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had about 20 girls there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And only four, I believe, survived, two of whom came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of the girls, unbeknownst to me, was keeping a diary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she was one of the very few people who were not liquidated with the liquidation of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was in hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a few days after the auction, they-- not the 'auction,' the action, they sniffed her out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was among a group of 11 people whom they took out of a bunker, and they marched to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they shot them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, before they did-- they, they shot her, she had her diary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she thrusted that diary into the hands of a Polish policeman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she says, before you kill me, you can take my life away, but please keep this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the first Jew you see after the war who comes to the cemetery to visit Radomsko or the cemetery, please give it to them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And sure enough, after the war, another friend whose husband had died during the-- from typhus during the ghetto came to Radomsko to visit his grave.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And an old woman approached her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This is the stuff that movies are made of.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "An old woman approached her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she says, don't ask me any questions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My son got this from somebody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they told me to give it to the first person I see who is Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she gave it to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that woman later on went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now, I have the typed original-- somebody typed.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
